    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:18.598" end="00:00:22.177">Uno, due. Uno, due, tre, quattro.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:22.255" end="00:00:23.496"/>
      <p begin="00:00:23.558" end="00:00:25.665">Se vi piace la musica di James Brown,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:25.665" end="00:00:27.557">questa serata vi piacer&#224;.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:27.557" end="00:00:29.731">Stasera si festeggiano i 62 anni di Black Velvet</p>
      <p begin="00:00:29.731" end="00:00:33.816">James Brown Junior!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:33.816" end="00:00:35.870" region="top">Whoo! 62! </p>
      <p begin="00:00:36.439" end="00:00:38.487" region="top">E allora adesso, battete le mani, </p>
      <p begin="00:00:38.487" end="00:00:39.718" region="top">perch&#232; abbiamo un giovane uomo </p>
      <p begin="00:00:39.718" end="00:00:41.503" region="top">che sta salendo sul palco. </p>
      <p begin="00:00:41.503" end="00:00:43.646">&#200; stato al David Letterman Show</p>
      <p begin="00:00:43.646" end="00:00:45.731">Applaudite, ecco a voi</p>
      <p begin="00:00:45.731" end="00:00:49.913">Black Velvet James Brown Junior!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:49.913" end="00:00:52.226"/>
      <p begin="00:00:52.226" end="00:00:53.898"/>
      <p begin="00:00:53.898" end="00:00:59.189">&#9834; &#200; un mondo di uomini &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:59.189" end="00:01:05.490">&#9834; Ma io non sarei niente, niente... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:01:05.490" end="00:01:06.648">Suono le canzoni di James Brown</p>
      <p begin="00:01:06.648" end="00:01:13.882">da quando avevo 14 anni.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:13.882" end="00:01:16.398"/>
      <p begin="00:01:16.398" end="00:01:17.857"/>
      <p begin="00:01:17.857" end="00:01:21.189"/>
      <p begin="00:01:21.189" end="00:01:25.774"/>
      <p begin="00:01:25.774" end="00:01:29.677">Ma ora suoner&#242; Charles Bradley.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:29.677" end="00:01:52.332"/>
      <p begin="00:01:52.486" end="00:01:54.356" region="top">Il mio primo album di canzoni originali </p>
      <p begin="00:01:54.356" end="00:01:58.013" region="top">uscir&#224; il 25 di gennaio. </p>
      <p begin="00:01:58.013" end="00:02:01.149">Ho lottato per 42 anni</p>
      <p begin="00:02:01.149" end="00:02:02.890">per cercare di farcela nell'industria musicale,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:02.890" end="00:02:04.606">e a 62 anni</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04.606" end="00:02:06.648">sto iniziando a trovare la mia strada.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:08.956" end="00:02:10.939">Non ho mai fatto abbastanza soldi</p>
      <p begin="00:02:10.939" end="00:02:13.794">per mantenermi nella musica.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.794" end="00:02:15.857">Ma spero che questo album</p>
      <p begin="00:02:15.857" end="00:02:17.304">sia il mio punto di svolta,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:17.304" end="00:02:20.111">che io possa mantenermi con la musica.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25.168" end="00:02:26.690">Ehi, amico,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:26.690" end="00:02:28.659">ti porto dell'acqua, ok?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28.659" end="00:02:30.004">Ehi, amico,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.004" end="00:02:30.683">questo &#232; il mio pappagallo.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.683" end="00:02:32.494">Mi fa arrabbiare.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:32.494" end="00:02:33.628">Mi arrabbio, me ne vado,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:33.628" end="00:02:35.364">vado nell'altra stanza, chiudo la porta,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:35.364" end="00:02:37.170">e lo lascio strillare quanto vuole.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:37.861" end="00:02:38.897">E ho un mio piccolo posto stabile,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38.897" end="00:02:40.429">non &#232; quello che voglio,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40.429" end="00:02:43.035">ma grazie a Dio ho un tetto sopra la testa.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:44.056" end="00:02:45.363">Quando entro nel mio piccolo appartamento</p>
      <p begin="00:02:45.363" end="00:02:46.945">e chiudo la porta,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:46.945" end="00:02:48.565">sono in pace.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:48.565" end="00:02:50.325">Ma attraversare le case popolari,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:50.325" end="00:02:53.051">entrare nell'ascensore,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:53.051" end="00:02:54.132">arrivare l&#224;..</p>
      <p begin="00:02:54.132" end="00:02:55.369">&#232; l&#236; che iniziano i problemi.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:55.369" end="00:02:56.898">Non sai mai</p>
      <p begin="00:02:56.898" end="00:02:58.994">cosa pu&#242; succedere in quelle serate.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:58.994" end="00:03:00.482">Il ragazzo di sotto,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:00.482" end="00:03:01.484">si chiama Alfred.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:01.484" end="00:03:03.022">Un bravo ragazzo, non d&#224; fastidio a nessuno.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:03.022" end="00:03:04.598">Un ragazzo di chiesa.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:04.598" end="00:03:06.544">Hanno sparato al suo appartamento.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06.544" end="00:03:07.565">Mi ha mostrato tutti i buchi</p>
      <p begin="00:03:07.565" end="00:03:08.289">dove hanno sparato.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:08.289" end="00:03:09.071">Gli ho detto "wow, amico"</p>
      <p begin="00:03:09.071" end="00:03:10.550">Gli ho detto</p>
      <p begin="00:03:10.550" end="00:03:12.823">"Uh, non potrei vivere al primo piano"</p>
      <p begin="00:03:12.823" end="00:03:14.391">Quando la situazione</p>
      <p begin="00:03:14.391" end="00:03:16.092">degenera nelle case popolari,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:16.092" end="00:03:17.808">vado a casa di mia madre</p>
      <p begin="00:03:17.808" end="00:03:19.537">e dormo nel suo seminterrato.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:31.862" end="00:03:33.477">Dunque vengo qui</p>
      <p begin="00:03:33.477" end="00:03:35.794">e mi fermo la notte,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:35.794" end="00:03:37.051">fino al giorno dopo,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:37.051" end="00:03:38.838">quando vengo ad occuparmi dell'area,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:38.838" end="00:03:39.884">a sistemare tutto</p>
      <p begin="00:03:39.884" end="00:03:43.414">per mantenere un tetto sopra le nostre teste.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:43.707" end="00:03:47.142">Mi piace fare delle palline</p>
      <p begin="00:03:47.142" end="00:03:48.735">di questo..</p>
      <p begin="00:03:50.722" end="00:03:53.068">Versarle qui.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:55.486" end="00:03:56.661">Ehi va bene cos&#236; il riso?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:56.829" end="00:03:58.127">Fammi vedere</p>
      <p begin="00:03:59.894" end="00:04:01.813">Ancora un po'.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:01.951" end="00:04:04.880">Vengo da una famiglia di 8 persone.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:04.942" end="00:04:07.772">Lo scopo principale &#232; tenere d'occhio tutto,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:07.772" end="00:04:11.547">&#232; mia madre e faccio del mio meglio.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:12.454" end="00:04:14.409" region="top">&#200; il mio bambino, </p>
      <p begin="00:04:14.409" end="00:04:16.520" region="top">e gli voglio bene. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:16.626" end="00:04:18.297" region="top">Mi lava i vestiti, </p>
      <p begin="00:04:18.467" end="00:04:19.206" region="top">pulisce questa casa. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:19.206" end="00:04:20.684" region="top">A San Valentino </p>
      <p begin="00:04:20.684" end="00:04:23.291" region="top">mi ha portato una scatola di caramelle. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:23.291" end="00:04:24.646" region="top">Dolce come quelle caramelle, </p>
      <p begin="00:04:24.646" end="00:04:25.871" region="top">ecco quant'&#232; dolce il mio bambino. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:25.871" end="00:04:27.567">Cerco solo</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27.567" end="00:04:28.273">di rendere la sua vita tranquilla,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:28.273" end="00:04:29.398">e</p>
      <p begin="00:04:29.398" end="00:04:31.440">cos&#236; non si deve preoccupare</p>
      <p begin="00:04:31.440" end="00:04:33.038">delle bollette e tutto il resto.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33.038" end="00:04:34.203">Mi sono fatto carico di tutto,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34.203" end="00:04:35.913">e davvero</p>
      <p begin="00:04:35.913" end="00:04:37.553">non sapevo a cosa andassi incontro.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:37.553" end="00:04:38.214">Ma ora ci sono dentro.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:38.214" end="00:04:39.802">Non cambier&#242;.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:39.802" end="00:04:40.970">Dunque l'unica cosa che posso fare</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40.970" end="00:04:42.685">&#232; cercar di far funzionare qualcosa,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:42.685" end="00:04:44.012">dove posso avere un'entrata decente</p>
      <p begin="00:04:44.012" end="00:04:46.923">e posso vivere e lasciar vivere.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:46.923" end="00:04:49.739">Ed &#232; tutto, posso chiedere una vita adesso.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:49.847" end="00:04:56.578"/>
      <p begin="00:04:56.578" end="00:05:00.314">&#9834; Andiamo sempre in giro. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:00.314" end="00:05:04.916">&#9834; Dove fermarsi, nessuno lo sa &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:04.916" end="00:05:08.256">&#9834; &#200; un mondo freddo &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:08.656" end="00:05:12.156">&#9834; &#200; un mondo freddo &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:13.939" end="00:05:15.856">&#9834; Come possiamo fermare i cambiamenti &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:15.856" end="00:05:20.897">&#9834; che accadono oggigiorno in America? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:30.701" end="00:05:34.686">&#9834; Ohhh, ohhh, ohhhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41.124" end="00:05:43.231">&#9834; Torna indietro &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43.231" end="00:05:46.939">&#9834; Torna indietro alla regola d'oro &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:46.939" end="00:05:48.645">&#9834; Oh, ah, uh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49.105" end="00:05:50.612">&#9834; torna indietro &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:50.612" end="00:05:55.148">&#9834; Torna indietro alla regola d'oro &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:55.148" end="00:05:57.856">&#9834; Butta gi&#249; tutto &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:57.856" end="00:06:11.472"/>
      <p begin="00:06:11.472" end="00:06:13.064">Questa &#232; una canzone</p>
      <p begin="00:06:13.064" end="00:06:15.023">dal nuovo album, No time for dreaming.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:15.023" end="00:06:16.148">Charles Bradley</p>
      <p begin="00:06:16.148" end="00:06:17.274">e la Menahan Street Band.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:17.274" end="00:06:18.731">Non posso credere</p>
      <p begin="00:06:18.731" end="00:06:20.064">che tu sia spuntato dal nulla</p>
      <p begin="00:06:20.064" end="00:06:22.273">come uno sconosciuto virtuale per noi.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:22.273" end="00:06:24.473">Hai gi&#224; registrato in passato?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:24.596" end="00:06:25.890">No.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:25.890" end="00:06:28.431">&#200; la prima volta, veramente, che esco allo scoperto.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:28.431" end="00:06:29.958">So che ti sei esibito.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:29.958" end="00:06:31.039">S&#236;.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:31.039" end="00:06:32.027">Come Black Velvet.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:32.027" end="00:06:33.649">S&#236;.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:33.649" end="00:06:34.939">Ed ora ti esibisci</p>
      <p begin="00:06:34.939" end="00:06:36.666">come Charles Bradley?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:36.666" end="00:06:37.677">S&#236;, s&#236;.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:37.677" end="00:06:38.898">Beh, di certo hai una band eccezionale</p>
      <p begin="00:06:38.898" end="00:06:39.728">che ti supporta.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:39.728" end="00:06:41.265">E, ovviamente,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:41.265" end="00:06:42.898">la gente al Daptone,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:42.898" end="00:06:44.058">sai,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:44.058" end="00:06:44.881">che gran gruppo!</p>
      <p begin="00:06:44.881" end="00:06:46.190">E hai visto</p>
      <p begin="00:06:46.190" end="00:06:48.866">cos'&#232; successo a Sharon Jones, S&#236;, s&#236;</p>
      <p begin="00:06:48.866" end="00:06:50.928">Chi, sai, come te</p>
      <p begin="00:06:50.928" end="00:06:52.469">&#232; passato dall'oscurit&#224; totale,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:52.484" end="00:06:55.048">chiss&#224; quali vette potrai scalare.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:55.048" end="00:06:56.455">Quindi</p>
      <p begin="00:06:56.455" end="00:06:58.647">questo dev'essere un momento emozionante per te..</p>
      <p begin="00:06:58.647" end="00:07:01.398">Credo che Dio abbia ascoltato le mie preghiere,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:01.398" end="00:07:03.440">davvero, del tipo</p>
      <p begin="00:07:03.440" end="00:07:05.606">mi sono chiesto perch&#232; ci sia voluto cos&#236; tanto,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:05.606" end="00:07:07.023">ma non puoi mettere in discussione Dio,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:07.023" end="00:07:08.981">quando Lui voglia fare qualcosa.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:08.981" end="00:07:11.915">Dunque alla mia veneranda et&#224; ha iniziato a girare.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:11.915" end="00:07:13.482">Cosa succeder&#224;?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:13.482" end="00:07:14.939">Nel senso, pensi in grande?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:14.939" end="00:07:16.706">Credo che il cielo sia il limite.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:16.706" end="00:07:18.981">Congratulazioni per questo magnifico album.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:18.981" end="00:07:20.296">Non importa cosa succeder&#224;,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:20.296" end="00:07:22.189">&#232; davvero un lavoro sopraffino.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:22.189" end="00:07:24.498">Charles Bradley per WFUV.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:24.667" end="00:07:27.897"/>
      <p begin="00:07:27.897" end="00:07:33.231">&#9834; Questo mondo che ormai sta bruciando &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:33.231" end="00:07:38.647">&#9834; E nessuno che vuole prendersi la colpa &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:38.647" end="00:07:43.821">&#9834; Non dirmi come devo vivere la mia vita &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:43.821" end="00:07:49.276">&#9834; Quando non hai mai provato quel dolore &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:49.276" end="00:07:55.314">&#9834; Ohhhhh Ahhhh Ohhhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:55.314" end="00:07:57.856">&#9834; Ohhhhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:57.856" end="00:08:00.569">&#9834; Non mi vedono che piango? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:00.569" end="00:08:02.400" region="top">&#9834; Ohhhhh &#9834; </p>
      <p begin="00:08:02.400" end="00:08:04.315"/>
      <p begin="00:08:04.315" end="00:08:05.564" region="top">Non so quanti artisti </p>
      <p begin="00:08:05.564" end="00:08:07.230" region="top">abbiano compiuto 62 anni </p>
      <p begin="00:08:07.230" end="00:08:08.955" region="top">e lanciato il loro primo album. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:09.722" end="00:08:11.458" region="top">Potrebbe essere il primo. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:12.284" end="00:08:14.441" region="top">Il ragazzo sta mettendo tutto in moto, </p>
      <p begin="00:08:14.441" end="00:08:16.440" region="top">per quanto mi riguarda. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:16.440" end="00:08:18.715" region="top">Ha lavorato sodo per tanto tempo, </p>
      <p begin="00:08:18.838" end="00:08:19.857" region="top">e spero </p>
      <p begin="00:08:19.857" end="00:08:21.232" region="top">che abbastanza persone riescano a sentirlo cantare, </p>
      <p begin="00:08:21.232" end="00:08:22.647">affinch&#232; possa avere</p>
      <p begin="00:08:22.647" end="00:08:23.856">la vita che ha sempre desiderato</p>
      <p begin="00:08:23.856" end="00:08:25.632">e prendersi cura della sua famiglia.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:25.632" end="00:08:27.118"/>
      <p begin="00:08:27.118" end="00:08:30.190">&#9834; Uh, S&#236; &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:30.190" end="00:08:32.606">&#9834; Ti prendo, ragazza &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:32.606" end="00:08:34.023">&#9834; S&#236; &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:34.023" end="00:08:36.125">&#9834; Solo te &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:36.125" end="00:08:37.814">Sono andato da Gabe</p>
      <p begin="00:08:37.814" end="00:08:39.981">perch&#232; pensavo che sapesse cosa stesse facendo.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:39.981" end="00:08:41.606">Credevo che potesse darmi una mano</p>
      <p begin="00:08:41.606" end="00:08:44.148">ad entrare nell'industria musicale.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:44.148" end="00:08:48.040">L'unica cosa che sapevo fare era salire sul palco e suonare.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:48.163" end="00:08:51.585">Se ti piace il funk e il soul, o l'afrobeat, e vivi a New York,</p>
      <p begin="00:08:51.693" end="00:08:54.500">Gabe Roth &#232; il ragazzo che vuoi nel retroscena.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:54.638" end="00:08:57.170">Questo &#232; il ragazzo che vuoi che ti indichi la strada da prendere,</p>
      <p begin="00:08:57.170" end="00:08:59.238">perch&#233; i suoi album erano fenomenali.</p>
